Well she'd give him his first. She'd put hers, and then the children, I'd come last. I m
ean it was a - a big difference in her bringing her children up and the way we were brought up. Oh yes. I mean however poor we were - we weren't allowed - for to - to say we don't want this and we don't that, if you didn't want it just leave it on the sid
e of your plate, and that was that.
